00:43:23,000 --> 00:43:24,700
<c.Japanese>理屈は分かるけど</c.Japanese>

502
00:43:28,866 --> 00:43:30,666
<c.Japanese>（女の子）え〜ん え〜ん…</c.Japanese>

503
