<c.Japanese>（女の子）え〜ん…</c.Japanese>

504
00:43:33,866 --> 00:43:35,000
<c.Japanese>（女）</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>押したら ダメでしょ？</c.Japanese>

505
00:43:35,066 --> 00:43:36,766
<c.Japanese>（女の子）</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>え〜ん え〜ん</c.Japanese>

506
00:43:40,300 --> 00:43:41,800
<c.Japanese>〝もう１人いる〞って…</c.Japanese>

507
00:43:43,666 --> 00:43:45,333
<c.Japanese>このことだったのかも</c.Japanese>

508
00:43:54,466 --> 00:43:57,366
<c.Japanese>昔 おばあちゃんに</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>言われた</c.Japanese>

509
00:43:59,400 --> 00:44:01,000
<c.Japanese>〝お前が 転ぶのは〞</c.Japanese>

510
00:44:01,233 --> 00:44:03,266
<c.Japanese>〝親から もらった</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>骨のせいじゃない〞</c.Japanese>

511
00:44:03,733 --> 00:44:06,166
<c.Japanese>〝お前が 歩き方を</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>知らないからだ〞って</c.Japanese>

512
00:44:10,200 --> 00:44:12,500
<c.Japanese>私は 遺伝子決定論を</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>支持しないわ</c.Japanese>

513
00:44:13,066 --> 00:44:16,533
<c.Japanese>殺人犯の子供が 全員</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>殺人を犯すわけじゃない</c.Japanese>

514
00:44:17,366 --> 00:44:18,200
<c.Japanese>人は環境によって</c.Japanese>

515
00:44:18,266 --> 00:44:19,500
<c.Japanese>変化し続けることのできる</c.Japanese>

516
00:44:19,566 --> 00:44:20,833
<c.Japanese>すごい生き物よ</c.Japanese>

517
00:44:25,000 --> 00:44:27,300
<c.Japanese>その言葉を</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>聞きたかったんだ</c.Japanese>

518
00:44:28,733 --> 00:44:29,633
<c.Japanese>ありがとう</c.Japanese>

519
00:44:34,166 --> 00:44:35,466
<c.Japanese>（</c.Japanese><c.Japanese><c.Japanese>勇樹</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>(</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>ゆうき</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>)</c.Japanese></c.Japanese><c.Japanese>）ママ〜</c.Japanese>

