521
00:44:43,600 --> 00:44:44,900
<c.Japanese>大丈夫よ きっと</c.Japanese>

522
00:44:47,400 --> 00:44:48,466
<c.Japanese>そうだな</c.Japanese>

523
00:44:54,266 --> 00:44:55,200
<c.Japanese>（美智子）行こう</c.Japanese>

524
00:44:58,800 --> 00:45:01,333
<c.Japanese>せっかくだから</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>ご飯でも食べて帰ろっか</c.Japanese>

525
00:45:03,400 --> 00:45:04,666
<c.Japanese>相手が俺で いいのかよ</c.Japanese>

526
00:45:05,433 --> 00:45:06,966
<c.Japanese>今日は 我慢する</c.Japanese>

527
00:45:31,633 --> 00:45:33,733
<c.Japanese>（</c.Japanese><c.Japanese><c.Japanese>藤崎</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>(</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>ふじさき</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>)</c.Japanese></c.Japanese><c.Japanese>）</c.Japanese>
