<c.Japanese>分かりました</c.Japanese>

530
00:45:37,133 --> 00:45:38,400
<c.Japanese>（</c.Japanese><c.Japanese><c.Japanese>島村</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>(</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>しまむら</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>)</c.Japanese></c.Japanese><c.Japanese>）</c.Japanese>
