<c.Japanese>疑ってるんですか？</c.Japanese>

531
00:45:38,466 --> 00:45:40,166
<c.Japanese>（藤崎）</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>正義が試されたと</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>思っています</c.Japanese>

532
00:45:40,266 --> 00:45:41,900
<c.Japanese>（石川）</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>お前を信じる価値が</c.Japanese>
