<c.Japanese>（</c.Japanese><c.Japanese><c.Japanese>西本</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>(</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>にしもと</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>)</c.Japanese></c.Japanese><c.Japanese>）</c.Japanese>
